---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------	Similar2Logo  v0.6	-----------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Changes
	- Adds following, passive, predation, randomwalk, segregation and virus examples
	- Adds a web GUI  

2. Bug fixes
	- Corrects assembly so that documentation is correctly added to the binary distribution.
	- Corrects the bogus documentation of the classes LogoSimulationParameters and LogoDefaultReactionModel.
	- Corrects reaction to ChangePosition influence in LogoDefaultReactionModel.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------	Similar2Logo  v0.5	-----------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Changes
	- Based on SIMILAR 0.2.5
	- Uses the optimized version of the probe AbstractProbeImageSwingJPanel of SIMILAR
	  in the class GridSwingView.
	- Add the probe LogoRealTimeMatcher to slow down simulations at a given rhythm.
	- Add a specific drawer for the boïds simulation. 
	- Add a documentation to describe the examples.

2. Bug fixes
	- Fixes pheromone dynamics.
	- Fixes the getNeighbors method of the class LogoEnvPLS.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------	Similar2Logo  v0.4	-----------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Bogus non-distributed release.


---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------	Similar2Logo  v0.3	-----------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Changes
	- Based on SIMILAR 0.2.4.
	- Add pheromone management.
	- Add heatbugs example.
	- Optimized perception model.

2. Bug fixes
	- Fixes various environment primitives.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------	Similar2Logo  v0.2	-----------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Changes
	- Add boïds, turmite and multiturmite examples.
	- Add a basic documentation.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------	Similar2Logo  v0.1	-----------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Initial release based on SIMILAR 0.2.4

